  "elapsed_s": 35.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He's only six months old, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He's around somewhere.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I'm sure you will.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was one of the intense moments of my life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not the-- the reunion was something my brother told me about, because it-- because it was a reunion from worldwide survivors, Kinder-- Kindertrans-- I'm sorry, Kindertransport, OK?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I mean, the children that-- that came to England-- actually, not just England.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came to England, Australia, United States, [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Canada, different parts of the world.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But anyway, this reunion was in England, and--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in '89.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a 50-year reunion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my wife-- my brother wanted to go to this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because in Israel, they-- of course, there was quite a few kids from-- from-- from Israel that went there, too.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think it was 100 kids that went from England-- from Israel, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was due for a trip anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never-- If I can, I like to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, if I can afford it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So yeah, that was a good excuse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This way, I meet my brother and everything else, and we make a whole trip out of it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "From England, we'll go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So at this reunion, we were-- the seating arrangement was according to countries-- Czechoslovakia, Poland, Austria, whatever, Belgium.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was a couple people I met, that-- that I knew from-- from-- from the-- the-- the boys' home.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
